{"type": "article", "id": 29110, "title": "会写时间的木钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T22:55:18Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160704171514kHKRPnY7l8zimy1t.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>木质时钟并不少见，今天要介绍的是一款能自己写下时间的时钟 Plock，由日本东北艺术工科大学的<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BellTreeNursing\" rel=\"nofollow\">鈴木完吾</a>设计制作。这个独具匠心的木钟在形状上借鉴了传统的自动化机械，但又没有将那些精致的细节隐藏起来，整个木钟由 407 块木质组件和 4 块作为动力来源的黄铜构成，看起来复杂庞大又不失精致。四支笔每分钟都会在磁性写字板上写下最新的时间，虽然字体并不是非常端正，但正是这种“瑕疵”更让人感受到创意背后精湛的手工艺。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tz7dH9DEADI\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>（需要科学上网）观看 Plock 运转起来的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070417153358YWyur7f0PeUTVG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691860\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607041715335OtU2Gg8u3NWlAj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658140\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704171533c2Zn4gGs5MVIhrCa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607041719022paUELtRHuxrsvyA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}